broken lance is a 1954 western film made by twentieth century-fox , directed by edward dmytryk and produced by sol c. siegel . the movie stars spencer tracy and features robert wagner , jean peters , richard widmark and katy jurado . shot in deluxe color and cinemascope , the film is a remake of house of strangers ( 1949 ) with the phillip yordan screenplay ( based upon the novel i 'll never go there any more by jerome weidman ) , transplanted out west , featuring tracy in the original edward g. robinson role , this time as a cowboy cattle baron rather than a lower east side italian immigrant banker in new york city .